    "In some cases, these techniques perform hierarchical learning in the input data and do not require human supervision.",
    "However, these techniques require a large amount of labeled data for observation, and it takes more time to analyze the noisy data.",
    "Moreover, their construction processes are complex.",
    "Thus, it is important to address various limitations presented in the traditional CNN to enhance the accuracy of motion intention prediction.",
    "So, a Res-LSTM technique is involved in the developed mechanism, and the newly implemented version is termed as AH-CNN-Res-LSTM."
